descript.abstract: This associative table resolves the many to many relationship between Soil Data Viewer folders and soil attributes (SDV rules).

idinfo.native: Microsoft Windows 7 Version 6.1 (Build 7601) Service Pack 1; Esri ArcGIS 10.1.1.3143

attr.attrdef: A integer value that uniquely identifies a soil attribute available in the Soil Data Viewer application.

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.

attr.attrdef: An integer value that uniquely identifies its corresponding folder.

metainfo.metstdn: FGDC Content Standard for Digital Geospatial Metadata
